2014-07~09
http://www.bangkokpost.com/opinion/opinion/433724/chinese-increase-tensions-in-xinjiang-region

Bangkok Post
Attacks on civilians are a crime and the state has a duty to investigate and prosecute those responsible. But Beijing seems uninterested in seriously probing these cases, the deeper causes of growing regional tensions, or reducing the repression it imposes on Uighurs, a predominantly Muslim, ethnically Turkic people in Xinjiang.

